Detailed Description

CmdInsertAnalyzerKit class is the insert command for tanalyzerkit nodes stored in the command stack.

CmdInsertAnalyzerKit represents a single tanalyzerkit insertion action on a scene, insert a new tanalyzerkit node to the scene.

CmdInsertAnalyzerKit::CmdInsertAnalyzerKit ( const QModelIndex &  parentIndex,
TAnalyzerKit *  analyzerKit,
SceneModel *  model,
QUndoCommand *  parent = 0 
)

Creates a new analyzerkit insert command that adds a analyzerkit node to a node given with the parentIndex node in the model.

If parent is not null, this command is appended to parent's child list and then owns this command.
